  "text": "Few years later, in 2015 Ye and Tang [CITATION_1] improved the results in Sun [CITATION_2] since they showed the existence of infinitely many small solutions with small negative energy to (P 0 ) by means of a new version of symmetric mountain pass lemma developed by Kajikiya [CITATION_3] with the non-negative potential",
